    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and has seen better days cosmetically, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a full restoration or a dedicated parts donor. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge at a great price, this is the one for you!",
