    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or someone in need of specific parts. Mechanically, the engine starts but has a noticeable misfire and several active oil leaks, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping when shifting between gears. The exterior shows its age with visible rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with faded paint and several dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with tears in the driver's seat and a non-functional climate control system. This car is sold as-is and will likely require towing to its destination.",
