    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely breathtaking condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service. It runs like a total dream and is ready for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
