      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, factory-original condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the dual-VANOS system has been precision-serviced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains rigid with a factory-spec subframe, and the M-variable differential lock ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless interior, this slicktop M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
